\id EZR
\h Ejira
\toc3 Ejr
\toc2 Ejira
\toc1 Nwer nyi Ejira
\mt1 Ejira
\is1 EZR - Ekajuk Unicode New Testament
\c 1
\s1 Sairus Yake anebe Isreel Ba bo bobo Ebta Feere Kehnge
\p 
\v 1 Go ngbokambang elya ni Sairus ntula Pesia, eji alum nya Jehova lˈlohko jol go nseenge nya Jeremaya bungu no, Jehova melle eltim ni Sairus ntula Pesia re á tiingi go ege nfam ejahbe, fere nyon nwer.
\p 
\v 2 Ji ji a ji Sairus ntula Pesia bungu no: <<Jehova Esowo bi li go ejahbetul ma-m ka ajahbe atul kpee nya li njini. Á ma-m yehke re me n si etahk Esowo ka-e go Jeusalem ji li go Juda.
\v 3 Nne ewe awohng awohng go egahne ellong, nong Esowo ebe jol a ne, nong á tahm go Jeusalem ji li go Juda, fere song si etahk Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, Esowo bi li go Jeusalem.
\v 4 Edi ajehng ajehng ji anebe Isreel ba bo bobo bo go ebta lene no, nong afono ejahbe bao ka bo asilva, a agul, a nsol eljen ebo, atohkondi, a ayare nya elkoro nya bo bahke koko si etahk Esowo go Jeusalem.
\p 
\v 5 Owo atubesi abangenahb nya Juda, a Benjamin, go abalimajom, a anebe Levi, nne awohng awohng no Esowo me-e kooro go eltim, toobo ebjing tahm go song si etahk Jehova go Jeusalem.
\v 6 Aneb ebjing ebo kpee kake bo ebo, ka bo nsol nyi bo ko asilva a agul lim, a nsol eljen ebo, a atohkondi, nsol nyi sahb kˈkim ekun, budu a ayare elkoro kpee.
\v 7 Asehnge sehnge ntula Sairus yehke nsol ba ka, nyi jolo go etahk Jehova, nyi ntula Nebukadneja yehke go etahk Jehova go Jeusalem tahm a nya, nya á rodo song bum go etahk esowo ebe.
\v 8 Sairus ntula Pesia tongo Mitredati ji jolo nkuuru akpohko, re á fange nsol nyia, fere faake kak Sesbaja ji ntubesi anebe Juda go abo, ye ji jolo ntubesi no anebe Juda.
\p 
\v 9 Nsol nyi a nyi bo ka bo: nkpingi agul jolo eltahl ewubu, nkpingi asilva jolo atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu, agbangngbang asilva jolo eltahl a ngbangngbang esehmwubu,
\v 10 akpeeke nya agul jolo eltahl ekpeeke ebwubu, akpeeke asilva nya jolo njad ebal jolo atahltahl ekpeeke ebwubu, a nsol eltul nyako nya jolo atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu.
\p 
\v 11 Nsol kpee nyi agul abola asilva jolo nsol atahltahl nkpel ewubal a nsol atahl awubu, Sesbaja ko go Babilon ba a nya go Jeusalem, a ane ba feere no kehnge.
\c 2
\s1 Nfange ane nyi feere no kehnge a Jerubabel
\p 
\v 1 A wo li abing ane ba lohng go esi ejahbe Juda ba bo bobo bo kak eju ba feere kehnge, ba Nebukadneja ntula Babilon bobo bo song kak eju go Babilon, bo feere kehnge Jeusalem a Juda, no nne feere go ege ejahbe.
\v 2 Atubesi ane ba a; Jerubabel, Jesua, Nehemaya, Seraya, Reelaya, Modekaya, Bilsan, Mispa, Bikvayi, Rehum, a Baana. Nfange aneblum Isreel ba feere kehnge ba a:
\p 
\v 3 Ebangenahb ji Paros jolo ane atahltahl nkpel elon, ane atahl anehkeni a ewubu ane abal (2172).
\v 4 Ebangenahb ji Sefataya, jolo ane atahlku era, a ewubu ane abal(372).
\v 5 Ebangenahb ji Ara jolo ane atahltahl, atahlku era ane elku (775)
\v 6 Ebangenahb ji Pahati-Moab etˈtohngo ji Jesua a Joab) jolo, ane atahltahl nkpel esehma, a ewubu ane abal (2812.
\v 7 Ebangenahb ji Elam, jolo ane atahltahl nkpel era ane atahl abal ane awubu ane ani (1254).
\v 8 Ebangenahb ji Jatu, jolo ane atahltahl nkpel abal, ane atahl asehma, a ane alon (945).
\v 9 Ebangenahb ji Jakayi jolo ane atahltahl, ane atahlku era (760).
\v 10 Ebangenahb ji Bani jolo, ane atahltahl, ane atahl ewubal ane abal (642).
\v 11 Ebangenahb ji Bebayi jolo ane atahltahl, ane atahl ewubu ajehng, a ane ara (623)
\v 12 Ebangenahb ji Ajigad jolo ane atahltahl nkpel era, a eltahl ane abal (1222).
\v 13 Ebangenahb ji Adonikam jolo ane atahltahl, ane atahl awubu era,a ane arakera(666)
\v 14 Ebangenahb ji Bikvayi jolo ane atahltahl nkpel elon, ane atahl abal,ane elku a nne awohng (2056).
\v 15 Ebangenahb ji Adin jolo ane atahltahl, ane atahl abal, ane awubu, ane ani(454).
\v 16 Ebangenahb ji Atersehng goji Hejekaya jolo ane atahlani ane elku era(98).
\v 17 Ebangenahb ji Bejayi jolo ane atahlku ajehng, ane ara(323).
\v 18 Ebangenahb ji Jora jolo ane atahl alon ane awubbal(112).
\v 19 Ebangenahb ji Hasum jolo ane atahl ewubu ajehng, a ane ara(223).
\v 20 Ebangenahb ji Gibar jolo ane atahl ani ane elku(95).
\v 21 Ane ba Betlehem jolo ane atahl arakera a ane ara(123).
\v 22 Ane ba Netofa jolo ane atahl abal ane elku a nne awohng(56).
\v 23 Ane ba Anatoti jolo ane atahl arakera ane anehkeni(128).
\v 24 Ane ba Ajimaveti jolo ane atahl abal ane abal (42).
\v 25 Ane ba Kiriati Jearim, Kefira, a Beeroti jolo ane atahltahl atahlku ebal, a ane ara(743).
\v 26 Ane ba Rama, a Geba jolo ane atahltahl ane atahl ewubu ajehng a nne awohng(621).
\v 27 Ane ba Mikmas jolo ane atahl arakera ane abal (122).
\v 28 Ane ba Betel, a ba Eai jolo ane atahl ewubu ajehng a ane ara (223).
\v 29 Ane ba Nebo jolo ane atahl abal ane awubu, ane abal (52).
\v 30 Ane ba Makbis jolo ane atahl asehma ane elku, a nne awohng (156).
\v 31 Ane ba Elam jolo ane atahltahl nkpel ara, a ane atahl abal, ane awubu, a ane ani(1254).
\v 32 Ane ba Harim jolo ane atahlku ajehng (320).
\v 33 Ane ba Lod,Hadid, a Ono jolo ane atahltahl atahlku ajehng, ane alon(725).
\v 34 Ane ba Jeriko jolo ane atahlku ebal ane alon(345).
\v 35 Ane ba Senaa jolo ane atahltahl nkpel esuwubu, a eltahl ane awubu(3630).
\p 
\v 36 Ebangenahb abalimajom: Go ebangenahb ji Jedaya, sehng go ebangenahb ji Jesua, jolo ane atahltahl nkpel ebal ane atahl anehkeni, ane awubu, a ane ara(973).
\v 37 Ebangenahb ji Imer jolo ane atahltahl nkpel ebal ane atahl ewubal, ane awubu ane abal(1052)
\v 38 Ebangenahb ji Pashur jolo ane atahltahl nkpel era, a ane atahl abal, ane asehma(1247).
\v 39 Ebangenahb ji Harim jolo ane atahltahl nkpel ebal, ane atahl awubu, a elku ane abal(1017).
\p 
\v 40 Anebe Levi: go ebangenahb ji Jesua abola Kadmiyel sehng ebangenahb ji Hodaviya, jolo ane atahl ara ane awubu, a ane ani(74).
\p 
\v 41 Abayimase: go ebangenahb ji Asaf jolo ane atahl arakera ane anehkeni(128).
\p 
\v 42 Ababˈbaabe ati mbu ba etahk Esowo: go ebangenahb ji Salum, a ji Ater, a ji Talmon, a ji Akub, a ji Hatita, a ji Sobayi bo jolo ane atahl arakera, ane elku eni(139).
\p 
\v 43 Alokeltum etahk Esowo: Ebangenahb ji Jiha, Hasufa, Tabaoti,
\v 44 Keros, Siaha, Padon,
\v 45 Lebana, Hagaba, Akub
\v 46 Hagab, Salmayi, Hanan,
\v 47 Gidel, Gahar, Reaya,
\v 48 Rejin, Nekoda, Gajam,
\v 49 Uja, Pasea, Besayi,
\v 50 Asna, Meunim, Nefusim,
\v 51 Bakbuk, Hakufa, Harhur,
\v 52 Bajiluti, Mehida, Harsa,
\v 53 Barkos, Sisera, Tema,
\v 54 Nejiya, a Hatifa.
\p 
\v 55 Ebangenahb ji alokeltum Solomon: ebangenahb ji Sotayi, Hasofereti, Peruda,
\v 56 Jaala, Darkon, Gidel,
\v 57 Sefatiya, Hatil, Pokeretis-hajebayim, a Ami.
\v 58 Alokeltum go etahk Esowo, a alokeltum ebangenahb ji Solomon jolo ane atahlku eni ane awubu, a ane abal.
\v 59 Ane baa lohng go ajahbe nyaa: Tel-mela, Telharsa, Kerub, Adon, a Imer. Ane baa maam tib abangenahb ebo go Isreel:
\v 60 Bo lohng go etˈtohngo ji Delaya, Tobaya, a Nekoda, jolo ane atahltahl ane atahl ewubal, a ewubu ane abal(652).
\p 
\v 61 Go ebangenahb ji abalimajom: ebangenahb ji Hobaya, Hakoji, a Bajilayi, nne no koo mmon no nkal no Bajilayi nnea Giled, bo fere jo lung-e mbing nyio.
\v 62 Bo sebe ebangenahb ji bo lohng no, bo tikem kahn. Owo wahng ka bo ki kpe taame re bo jol abalimajom. Bo yehke bo go ellong abalimajom, tibre bo bumu bo ana ane ba ki li saang
\v 63 Nfili ejahbe tongo bo re, bo kˈkpe ka bo nsol nyi sahb lˈli saang, nyi kpo lohng go njom alimi, tete jol re nlimanjom ebjol no bahke tubu elfaange nsol nyi bo kpo lung re Urim a Tumim.
\p 
\v 64 Ane kpee ba feere kehnge jolo: ane atahltahl nkpel atahl alon a nkpel elon, a ane atahlku era(42360),
\v 65 budu o jolo alokeltum ba nkal a ba nlum ane atahltahl nkpel elku era, a ane atahl arakera, ane elku ebal(7337), a abayimase anebkal a aneblum jolo atahl awubu.
\v 66 Bo bele ebvankang atahltahl atahlku mbvankang anyehng, a mbvankang elku anyehng(736), mbvankang anyˈnya jolo atahl ewubbal, a mbvankang anyˈnya eblon (245),
\v 67 Akamel jolo atahltahl, a eltahl ekamel elku, ebvankang jolo atahltahl nkpel elku anyehng, a mbvankang atahlku ajehng(6720).
\p 
\v 68 Ngare nyi bo ma rehng go etahk Jehova go Jeusalem, egom atubesi abangenahb wehre abo ka go eltum ni bo jo seb re bo tuungu etahk Esowo si, edi jˈnehm.
\v 69 Ntubesi awohng awohng ka ana á bahke ma ka, akpohko nya bo ka no jolo agul ekilo atahltahl atahl alon, (500 kilos). Nya asilva jolo akilo atahltahl nkpel esehma ekilo atahl awubu, (3000). Bo ka akpawobo atahl alon nya abalimajom.
\p 
\v 70 Abalimajom, anebe Levi, abayimase, ababˈbaabe abuga, a alokeltum go etahk Esowo, bo feere song lene go ebo ajahbe, a nlong ane bako, erik anebe Isreel bako feere song jol go ebo ajahbe.
\c 3
\s1 Ane Kpe Tuungu Egudu Njom Lim
\p 
\v 1 Eji ba rehng nnyahng esehma, fvfo anebe Isreel bob song ji go ebo ajahbe, bo kehm ba kono edi ajehng, go eltim anehng go Jeusalem.
\v 2 Owo Jesua mmona Jojadak, a abalimajom bako ba bo kpo lim eltum ano, a Jerubabel mmona Seltiel a ane ba bo kpo lim eltum ano, kehme ellimi edi njom ji Esowo bi Isreel re bo jo lim njom eljahme fi o, ana bo nyono go ntahm nyi Mosis nlokeltum no Esowo.
\v 3 Jol eji bo jo fˈfahl agburu ajahbe nya li sennge bo kak, bo limi egudu njom kunu go nkˈkula nnahb ekahme nyi tohko jol. Bo kehme ajom eljahme fi ka Jehova lim o, ajom nya efungfu a ajom nya elgung.
\v 4 Bo limi Elkak ni Nkpatahk, a mfange njom eljahme fi, ana bahke jo jol efung abehng abehng, toono ana bo nyono go nwer atahm.
\v 5 Eji jio ma sehng bo jo limi njom nyi bo kpo jahm fi nyi bo kpo kono ellimi, a ajom nya ebareka nfenfe, a ajom nya li ka ajoobo nkak nya Jehova, a nsol nyi ane jo ka Jehova go eboa ntim.
\v 6 Go ngbokambang efung bi nnyahng esehma, wo bo bomo ajom alimi nya bo kpo jahm fi ka Jehova, jol ngare nyia nnahb ekahme nyi etahk Esowo bo ka bum.
\s1 Ane Bomo Eltuungu Etahk Esowo Si
\p 
\v 7 Owo bo kehm kake abalange ntahk a abakumu ntahk akpohko, fere ka anebe Sidon a Taya nsol alehke, amahm a akehng oliv, eji bo lˈko akv nti aseda sehng aya ma nne lˈkˈ ma nyehn egbuk jehko go Lebanon ba rehng Jopa ana Sairus ntula Pesia fa bo nnyo.
\p 
\v 8 Eji ma rehng nnyahng ebal go etoono elya ni bo ba rehng go etahk Esowo go Jeusalem, Jerubabel mmona Seltiyel, Jesua mmona Jojadak, a erik ane bako, abalimajom a anebe Levi, a ane kpee ba kpehna kehnge eju ba rehng go Jeusalem, bomo eltum, yehke anebe Levi ba ma rehng nnya eltahl asongo go ero, re bo jo kpur eltum etahk Jehova.
\v 9 Ane baa ba jo kpur eltum etahk Esowo. Jesua a abon ebe, a abonanyehn, a Kadmiyel a abon ebe, ba lohng go ebangenahb ji Hodaviya, a abon ba Henadad, a abon ebo, a abonanyehn, bo kpee anebe Levi, bo kodo abo jo kpur anebe eltum etahk Esowo.
\p 
\v 10 Eji asehketahk ma bum nnahb ekahme etahk Jehova mal, owo abalimajom kehm liibi akpawobo ebo, kehm fere jo wor atang ebo. Anebe Levi go ebangnahb ji Asaf kehm rodo akpalekpale agbanggbang nya ase akubu, bo kehm mehle yiimi ebo adi, kehm kehme elyimi tehk Jehova, ana Devid ntula Isreel tibi bo.
\v 11 Ana bo kpˈtehke fere jo kak saam, bo yimi ese jia ka Jehova. <<Jehova kpˈnobo! Elkoro ene ni á kpi anebe Isreel li go njinanjini!>>. Owo ane kpee kehm rabe egburu elrabe jo tehk Jehova, tibre bob bum nnahb ekahme etahk Jehova.
\v 12 Wo egom abalimajom ba ga kul, a anebe Levi a atubesi abangenahb bo ji nyehne etahk Esowo ji mahne mahne, kehm lingi wahre wahre eji bo nyehne nnahb ekahme nyia nyi bo ma bum, egom jehko gbalee jo rabe go eyebatahng.
\v 13 Nnene maam yab ewahl eyebatahng a ji eling, tibre ewahl ane wahre sehng. Ane jo wuku ewahl go fee.
\c 4
\s1 Anebekv kpane eltuungu etahk Jehova si
\p 
\v 1 Eji anebekv ba Juda, a Benjamin wuku re anebe Isreel ba woomo eju ebfeere kehnge ba kehme etahk Jehova Esowo bi Isreel si,
\v 2 bo kehm bake goji Jerubabel, a atubesi abangenahb, kehm ba tong bo re, <<Nong wahr tob-n go elsehke, tibre e kpo loko Esowo ebahne ana wahn, fvfo e kpo lim njom ka-e, bomo ngare nyi Esarhadon ntula Asiria, ye ji ko-r ba.
\p 
\v 3 Wo Jerubabel, Jesua, a erik atubesi abangenahb nya Isreel kehm faange re, wahn ebo abehng abehng ń kpimm anahre go elsehke etahk Esowo ebahre. Wahr ntahng ntahng bahke sehke etahk ka Jehova Esowo Isreel, ana Sairus ntula Pesia ka-r elkahn.
\p 
\v 4 Owo ane ba jolo sennge bo kak, kehm kehme anebe Juda nwoono kak go bo a ntim, lim bo bel elfahle go elsehke.
\v 5 Bo lake atubelle bo jo song kak anebe Isreel nkpaale go eboa ntoobo, fere bvvrv atoobo ebo, bomo ngare nyi Sairus ntula Pesia jo fili edi, tete song rehng ngare nyi Dairus ntula Pesia jo fili edi.
\s1 Elkpane Ni Anebekv Kpe Kpan Go Eltuungu Jeusalem Si Ngare Nyi Ntula Ahasuaros a
\p 
\v 6 Ngare nyi Ahasuaros bomo elfili Pesia, anebekv ba Juda kehm nyono nwer nyi bo bungu ebi bade anebe Juda a Jeusalem.
\p 
\v 7 Go afung nya Ataseses ntula Pesia, Bislam, Mitredati, Tabeel a erik anebe eltum ebe nyono nwer tv ntula Ataseses. Nwer nyio bo nyono go alum ejahbe Aram, fvfo eljini elnyono ni anebe Aram.
\p 
\v 8 Rehum ntubesia nsoja , a Simsayi nnyeela awer nyono abi nsol go nwer bada Jeusalem tum tv ntula Ataseses ana wo á yeele no:
\v 9 Nwer nyia lohng goji Rehum ntubesi nsoja, Simsayi nnyeele awer, a ane ba bo kpo lim eltum ano, abalamalam, a atubesi ba ane ba lohng go Tripolis, anebe Pesia, Erek, Babilon, a anebe Susa ji li Elam,
\v 10 a ellong ane bako ba ebgburu ntula Asiria Asubanipal no kpi ellub ko bo ba, fere ba ka bo edi ellene go ejahbe ji Samaria, a adi nyako, go erede mfam, aya ma Yufritis re bo jol.
\p 
\v 11 Nwer nyi a, nyi bo nyono no tum tv-e: Ntul Ataseses, wahr ji wob-a go elwo erede bi aya ma Yufritis.
\v 12 E kpˈsebe re ntul kahn re, anebe Ju ba lohngo go ega ba rehng go egahre, bob rehng go Jeusalem, bo kpˈtuungu ntahnsi a ebˈbi ejahbe si. Bo kpˈtuungu nnahb ekahme bum fere si akahme.
\v 13 E kpˈsebe re, ntul tob kahn re, bo lˈtuungu ejahbe jia si, fere tob si akahme nyaa kpee mal, bo nehm kpe kpi etak ka-a, afi ntahbe anyehng anyehng, wahng ka akpohko nya jol bake goji ntul, nehm kpe ba.
\v 14 Eji e wob go ega elwo, ana alokeltum eba, fvfo e nehme seb re nne awohng awohng daang-a, e kpˈtumu etib bia tv, re wahr lim ntul kahn,
\v 15 eji bo lˈsong feede go edi nsol akuuru ji ane ba ma tohko jol nji nyia wo kehm bake. Wo go nsol nyi bo nyono mahne bum, a bahke nyehne re ejahbe jia ntahnsi ejahbe ji, bob ka atul agbiingi a arohko ajahbe, ebjol ntahnsi ejahbe mahne mahne. Jia ji wahngka bo rannge ejahbe jia.
\v 16 E kpˈtongo ntul re, bo lˈsi ejahbe jia, fere lang akahme enye, ejumjum nehm kpe jol ka-a erede mfam aya ma Yufritis.
\p 
\v 17 Ntul kehm tumu mfaange nyia: Tv Rehum ji ntubesia nsoja, Simsayi ji nnyeele awer, a ane ba bo kpo lim eltum ano ba lene go Samaria, a adi nyako go erede mfam aya ma Yufritis. M ma-n kak nnyo.
\v 18 Nwer nyi ń tumu tv-r, bob lung fere tooro ana lohngo no go egame esamahr.
\v 19 N ka nsahm bob feede, fere seb kahn re ejahbe jia eblim afemfem bade atul nkpela nkpele, fvfo ejahbe jia bob rur atahnsi ane a anebe atongtong.
\v 20 Jeusalem bˈbel atahntahn atul, ba jo fili erede ejang bia bi aya Yufritis, ane jo kpi atak a atahbe nyako ka bo.
\v 21 Anv ka elkahn, bo tong ane baa, bo rahke eltum, eji bo lˈkˈkpe tuungu ejahbe jio si, tete n fa bo nnyo.
\v 22 Kunu ekpu, nong ntong nyia ki-a kpaale. Ka taame ntong nyia nyange ko mfem ba ka ntul.
\p 
\v 23 Ana bo lungu ekpake nwer jia ji ntula Ataseses ka Rehum, Simsayi nyeela nwer, a ane ba bo kpo lim eltum ano, bo kehm mehle tvtv song kpiri anebe Ju go Jeusalem, song sahde bo go egban.
\p 
\v 24 Ano wo, bo laange eltum etahk Esowo go Jeusalem tete go etoono elya ni Dairus ma jol ntula Pesia.
\c 5
\s1 Nwer nyi Tatenayi nyono tv Darios
\p 
\v 1 Ngare nyio Hagayi nnyehnamahr, a Jakaraya nnyehnamahr ye ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Edo, bo jo nyehne amahr tong anebe Ju ba jolo go Juda a Jeusalem, go mbing nyi Esowo bi Isreel, ye ji jo fili bo.
\v 2 Owo Jerubabel mmona Seltiyel, a Jesua mmona Jojadak bomo eltuungu etahk Esowo go elsehke go Jeusalem. Abanyehnamahr Esowo jolo abo jo kak bo ebo.
\p 
\v 3 Ngare nyio Tatenayi ji jolo nfili ejahbe no erede ejang bi aya ma Yufritis, a Setar-Bojenayi, a ane ba bo kpo lim eltum ano, kehm ba bahb bo re, <<Nne awo ka-n nsahm re wahn tuungu etahk Esowo jia si, fere lim mal ana?>>
\v 4 Bo tob bahbe bo re, <<Abing aneblum ba na ba kpˈsehke etahk jia?
\v 5 Wo elmahr ni Esowo Ju jo seenge anebkul Ju, owo wahng ka atubesi abalimeltum Pesia ki ma sahde bo, tete atubesi abalimeltum Pesia nyon nwer tv Darios, fere ko mfaange go ege.
\p 
\v 6 Nwer nyi a, nyi Tatenayi nfili ejahbe no erede ejang aya ma Yufritis, Setar-Bojenayi, a ane ba bo kpo lim eltum ano, a atubesi abalimeltum ba erede ejang aya ma Yufritis, tumu tv ntula Darios:
\v 7 Ntooro a nnyo mi bo tumu tv-e mi a: Ntula Darios: E ma-a kak nnyo.
\v 8 <<E kpꞌsebe re ntul kahn re, e je go ejahbe Juda, fere je go etahk Esowo bi gbale sehng. Ane kpꞌsehke etahk Esowo jio, bo kpˈkoko agburu atal jo lang. Agburu ajangnti nya bo kpꞌkoko kunu akahme. Bo kpꞌkake eko go eltum nia, fvfo eltum kpꞌjene elwaare ana atubesi Ju kpi bo tib.
\v 9 <<Wahr ebbahb anebkul re, <Nne awo ka-n nsahm re wahn tuungu etahk Esowo jia si , fere lim mal ana?>
\v 10 E tob bahbe abing ebo, eji elˈnyon fere tum abing atubesi ebo tv-a.
\v 11 Ana wo bo faang-r no: <<Wahr alokeltum Esowo bi limi elbung abola ndi ba, e kpˈtuungu etahk jia si, ji bo si aya tvv nya ma sehng, ji egburu ntul awohng go Isreel si no mal.
\v 12 Wo eji babnsoo limi Esowo bi li ejahbetul bel erakatahng, á faake bo ka Nebukadneja nnea Kaldia ntula Babilon go abo, ye wo rannge etahk Esowo jia, fere kpu ane tahm eju go Babilon.
\v 13 Wo go ngbokambang elya ni Sairus ntula Babilon, ntula Sairus kaa ejehke re, bo tuungu etahk Esowo jia si.
\v 14 Jol á tob yehke nsol nyi bo ko agul lim, a nsol nyi bo ko asilva lim nya Nebukadneja yehke go Etahk Esowo ji li Jeusalem, song bum go etahk asowo ebo go Babilon. Ntul Sairus yehke nsol nyio go etahk asowo ebo go Babilon, faake kak nne no bo jo lung-e re Sesbaja go ebo, ye ji á yehk-e re á jol nfili ejahbe ji Juda.
\v 15 Fvfo ntul tongo re, rod nsol nyia wo song bum go etahk Esowo go Jeusalem edi ji jolo no. Wo fere tuungu etahk Esowo si edi ji jolo mahne mahne.
\v 16 Owo Sesbaja jia kehm ba bum nnahb ekahme nyi etahk Esowo go Jeusalem. Bomo efung bio tete rehng anv, bo kpi nlimi nlimi eltum etahk Esowo, ka mal.>>
\v 17 Lˈfere yebe ntul atahng, nong á ka nsahm bo feede go edi ekuuru nsol ntul go Babilon, wo nyehn joare ntula Sairus nyˈnyon nwer tong re bo feere song tuungu etahk Esowo si go Jeusalem. Nong ntul fere tum mfaange enye tv-r ana á kpˈtiri re wahr lim go ntong nyia.
\c 6
\s1 Bo Sebe Nyehn Ejehke Ji Sairos Ka No
\p 
\v 1 Ntula Darios ka ejehke, bo song feede go edi ekuuru nsol ntul go Babilon.
\v 2 Bo kehm nyehne nwer nyi bo fehde go edi ji bo kpo kuuru nsol ebta go mfam nyi Ekbatana go ejang ejahbe Media, ana wo bo nyono no: Ejum elbuumu ji a:
\v 3 Go ngbokambang elya ni ntula Sairus, ntula Sairus ka ejehke bo nyon nwer bade etahk Esowo ji li go Jeusalem re: Nong bo tuungu etahk Esowo si, jol go edi ji anebe Ju jo lim ajom ebo. Nong bo si go nnahb ekahme nyi mahne mahne. Bahke wahre rehng ntahme atahl abal a ntahme elon, akpang bahke tob jol ntahme atahl abal a ntahme elon.
\v 4 Bo lˈlang agburu atal nkpa era, ajangenti jol elkpa anehng. Ekun bi bo bahke kpiki, bahke lohngo ebam ntul.
\v 5 Fvfo nsol nyi bo ko agul lim, a nsol nyi bo ko asilva lim nya etahk Esowo nya ntula Nebukadneja rodo go etahk Esowo ji li Jeusalem, ko ba go Babilon, ḿ bahke feere a nya song bum go etahk Esowo go Jeusalem, adi nya jolo no, bo bahke song bum go etahk Esowo.
\s1 Ntula Dairios Ka Ejehke Re Bo Soro Asi Go Eltum Etahk Esowo
\p 
\v 6 Owo Tatenayi nfili ejahbe no erede ejang aya Yufritis, a Setar-Bojenayi, a wahn ji kpo lim eltum ano ejang ejahbe jia, kaan eyake o.
\v 7 Kana lim mfem, go eltum etahk Esowo nia. Nong nfili ejahbe no anebe Ju a anebkul ba anebe Ju tuungu etahk Esowo jia si edi ji jolo no mahne mahne.
\p 
\v 8 Anv, n kp-n kake ejehke ejum ji ń bahke limi ka anebkul baa ba anebe Ju go eltum etahk Esowo nia ni bo kpˈsehke:
\p Ekun bi ḿ bahke kpiki anebe eltum kpee, bahke lohngo go ebam ntul. Yehken go akpohko nya ḿ ma ko atak go erede ejang ajahbe ji aya ma Yufritis, eji eltum lˈkˈrahke.
\v 9 Ajehng ajehng ji bo kpꞌsebe, abon nfong ba nlum, ekom, a abon ekom, nya bo bahke koko jo lim ajom nya bo kpo jahm fi, ka Esowo bi li go ero, fvfo awid, akang, amahm a akehng, ana abalimajom ba Jeusalem bahbe no, ḿ bahke tiki jo ka bo efung abehng abehng kꞌkane.
\v 10 Eji bo lˈmal jo lim ajom ebo nya bahke jo yebe Esowo bi li ejahbetul atahng, fere jo kak ero ka ntul re jo nob a ne, a abon ebe.
\p 
\v 11 Fvfo budu o, me n ka ejehke re, nne awohng awohng no lˈyaange ejehke jia, nong bo yehke ewaade go ege etahk, subu rod jahm, rod-e tung ewaade á tokko o, tib esi ebi ejum ji á limi no, etahk eje bo bahke limi jol ebimbim.
\v 12 Nong Esowo bi ma yehke re mbing enye jol go Jeusalem, rannge ntul awohng awohng afi jolo ane ba bahke mehle ebo re bo yahke yaange ejehke jia, afi fere rannge etahk Esowo jia go Jeusalem. Me, Darios wo ma ka elkahn nia. Nong bo lim jang jang ana m bungu no.
\s1 Bob Si Etahk Esowo Mal Fere yake Ka Esowo
\p 
\v 13 Wo, tib esi ejehke ji ntula Darios tumu no, Tatenayi nfili ejahbe no ejang erede aya ma Yufritis, Setar-Bojenayi, a ane ba bo kpo lim eltum ano, bo limi jangjang ana ntul bungu no.
\v 14 Ano wo anebkul ba anebe Ju soro asi jo si etahk Esowo, eltum nio jo jene elwaare. Hagayi nnyehnamahr, a Jakaraya ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Edo jo nyehn amahr jo kak bo eltim. Bo si etahk Esowo mal, ana Esowo bi Isreel ka Isreel elkahn, a ajehke nya Sairus, Darios, a Ataseses atul ba Pesia.
\v 15 Bo male etahk Esowo go elsehke, go efung bi kpꞌbiingi nfung era nnyahng mi Adar. Go nnya erakera nyi ntula Dairus kpi ejahbe fili.
\p 
\v 16 Owo anebe Isreel, abalimajom, anebe Levi, a anebe Isreel ba woomo eju, limi elkak ni bo rodo etahk Esowo jia ka Esowo go eyebatahng.
\v 17 Ana bo rodo etahk jia ka Esowo, enyam bi a bi bo wulu lim ajom, alum efong atahl alon, ekom atahl awubu, abon ekom atahltahl. Go njom nyi abiafem nya anebe Isreel kpee bo ko ewubu afahmbul ebbal. Efahmbul ajehng go etꞌtohngo ajehng.
\v 18 Owo bo yehke abalimajom bum go ebo adi ntum, a anebe Levi bum nlong a nlong, re bo lim eltum Esowo go Jeusalem, ana bo nyono go nwer nyi Mosis.
\s1 Bo limi elkak Ni Elsehng Sa
\p 
\v 19 Go ngbokambanga nnyahng, ewubu a nfung eni, anebe Isreel ba ma kehnge eju limi elkak ni Elsehng Sa.
\v 20 Abalimajom, a anebe Levi, ejum aka ajehng ajehng go ebo agubjing kpee limm. Anebe Levi kehm wulu njoro nyi elkak ni Elsehng Sa ka anebe Isreel kpee ba ma kehnge eju, ka abonanyehn ba li abalimajom, fere tob ka bofono antahng.
\v 21 Owo anebe Isreel ba kpehna kehnge eju kehm lehke nsol njom, a ane bako kpee ba ma yab elbo go nsol aka anyehng anyehng nyi ane ba ki li Ju kpo lim, re bo kak Jehova Esowo bi Isreel.
\v 22 Bo ko nfung esehma lim elkak ni abred nya bo kil jo kak ayist go eyebatahng, tibre ntim ebo ebrur go eyebatahng ji Jehova ka bo eji á yaange ntir atahng nyi ntula Siria bada bo, eji á kake bo ebo go eltum etahk Esowo, Esowo bi anebe Isreel.
\c 7
\s1 Ejira feere ba rehng go Jeusalem
\p 
\v 1 Eji aya tvv ma sehng, ngare nyi Ataseses ntula Pesia kpi edi fili, nnenlum awohng jolo go no bo jo lung-e re Ejira. Á jolo mmona Seraya, ji mmona Ajariya, ji mmona Hilkaya,
\v 2 ji mmona Salum, ji mmona Jadok, ji mmona Ahitub,
\v 3 ji mmona Amariya, ji mmona Ajariya, ji mmona Meraoti,
\v 4 ji mmona Jerahiya, ji mmona Uji, ji mmona Buki,
\v 5 ji mmona Abisua, ji mmona Finehas, ji mmona Elieja, ji mmona Eron ji ntubesi nlimanjom.
\v 6 Ejira jia lohng go Babilon. Á jolo ntˈtibi, á jolo nne no bele elkahne atahm nya Mosis gbalee, nya Jehova Esowo bi Isreel ka Isreel. Ntul ka-e ejum ajehng ajehng ji á bahb-e no, tibre ebo bi Jehova Esowo ebe jolo a ne.
\v 7 Egom anebe Isreel budu, abalimajom, anebe Levi, abayimase, ababꞌbaabe ati mbu, a alokeltum go etahk Esowo, fvfo tob ba go Jeusalem, eji ma yel nnya esehma nyi ntul Ataseses kun etul.
\p 
\v 8 Ejira ba rehnge Jeusalem go nnyahng elon mi elya ni kpˈbiingi nnya esehma nyi ntula Ataseses kun etul.
\v 9 Á bomo eljen ene go Babilon asongo, go ngbokambang efung bi ngbokambanga nnyahng, song rehng go Jeusalem go ngbokambang efung bi nnyahng elon, tib nnoobo ebo bi Esowo ebe jolo a ne.
\v 10 Tibre Ejira rodo elne kak jo kpili atahm, fere jo bum atahm nya Jehova, fere jo tib ajehke a atahm go Isreel.
\s1 Nwer nyi Ntula Ataseses Nyono Tv Ejira
\p 
\v 11 Nwer nyi a nyi ntul Ataseses tumu tv Ejira ji nlimanjom a ntˈtibi, nne no kpi ngbere go nsol nyi li bade elkahn a ajehke nya Jehova kaa Isreel:
\p 
\v 12 Me Ataseses, ntul no atul, n kpˈnyono tv Ejira ji nlimanjom, a ntˈtibi no atahm nya Esowo bi li ejahbetul: N kp-a kake nnyo.
\v 13 N kpi ejehke jia ka re, nnea Isreel awohng awohng no li go egame ejahbe, abalimajom, anebe Levi, no kp-e koro re á feere kehnge go Jeusalem a na, bahke ma song.
\v 14 Wo wo ntul kp-a tumu a ane asehma ba kpo tub-e elle, re wahn song feede kahn ji li go Juda, a Jeusalem, bade atahm Esowo eba nya wob-a go ebo.
\v 15 Esehnge sehnge ḿ bahke rodo asilva a agul, nya ntul a abatubu elle ebe ma ka Esowo bi Isreel go elkoro, ye ji edi ellene eje li go Jersalem,
\v 16 budu a asilva kpee a agul, nya ḿ bahke bele go ejang bi Babilon, a nsol nyi ane a abalimajom ka go ebo eltim, tib eltum etahk Esowo ebo go Jeusalem.
\v 17 Go akpohko nyaa kunu ekpu wo gunu alum efong, ekom, abon ekom, budu a ajom nya amohk nti, a ajom nya amahm, ko bo song lim njom go egudu njom ji etahk Esowo ebahne ji li Jeusalem.
\v 18 Wo, a anebe Ju abonane ebahne, ḿ bahke ma ko erik asilva a agul lim ejum ajehng ajehng ji kpꞌnobo, jang jang ana ntir nyi Esowo ebahne li no.
\v 19 Yake ka Esowo bi Jeusalem, nsol kpee nyi bo ma faake kak-n go abo, nyi ḿ bahke jo ko kak Esowo go etahk Esowo ebahne.
\v 20 Wo ejum ajehng ajehng jehko ji ń kpꞌsebe re wahn ko lim eltum etahk Esowo ebahne, ji tiki li re wahn ka ane bo ko lim eltum, ḿ bahke ma yehke akpohko go elkohl ntul.
\p 
\v 21 Me, ntula Ataseses, n kpꞌtumu ejehke tv abakuuru akpohko ntul go ejang ejahbe ji aya ma Yufritis re ajehng ajehng ji Ejira, nlimanjom, a ntꞌtibi no atahm Esowo bi ejahbetul lꞌbahb-n,
\v 22 asilva ekilo atahltahl nkpel enehkeni ekilo atahl awubu, nkohl nyi bo kpo lung re, awid jolo ekilo atahltahl eltahl a nkpel elon, nsang amahm jolo nsang atahl alon , nsang akehng oliv, jolo nsang atahl alon, akang kaan bo ana bo sebe no.
\v 23 Ejum ajehng ajehng ji Esowo bi li go ero kpˈsebe go eltum etahk eje, nong wahr limen nobnob, go esi ji etahk Esowo bi li go ero. Jenji wahnge e bahke taame re erakatahng ji Esowo gbo tub ejahbe ji ntul kpˈfili, a abon ebe?
\v 24 Fvfo kahn-n re, wahn nsahm ń kpimm nyi ḿ bahke koko etak a ntahbe anyehng anyehng goji abalimajom, anebe Levi, abayimase, ababꞌbaabe ati mbu, a alokeltum etahk Esowo afi abalimeltum bako go etahk Esowo jia.
\p 
\v 25 Fvfo wo, Ejira ko ngbere nyi Esowo eba, nyi li ana, wo yehke atubesi abalame ane, fere yehke abalamalam re bo jo lam atingi alam ka ane bao kpee go ejang aya ma Yufritis, bo kpee ji kpꞌkahne atahm nya Esowo eba. Fvfo ḿ bahke fere jo tib ane ba kil elkahne atahm nyaa.
\v 26 Nne awohng awohng no tohko bum ntahm Esowo eba, a ntahm nyi ntul, bo bahk-e tiki ka erem bi ewul, afi kam-e yehke go ejahbe, afi taare nsol enye, afi kake ngbekobo.
\s1 Ejira tehke Jehova
\p 
\v 27 Ejira kehm bungu re, <<Eltehke jol ka Jehova, ye ji li Esowo bi babnsoo ebahre, ye ji kake elkohn ejum ana jia go eltim ntul, re á kpunu etahk Jehova ji li go Jeusalem go elkohn mbang ana nyia.
\v 28 Nong eltehke jol ka ye, ye ji ma tanne nnoobo ebo ebe kun-m, eji n yiimi go esamahr ntul, abatubu elle ebe, a atahntahn ane kpee ba kpo lim eltum a ntul. Tib eji ebo bi Jehova Esowo ebame jolo aname, m bele etahneltim ji n lungu ane ba jolo atubesi ane go Isreel ba wane, re bo je aname.
\c 8
\s1 Atubesi Ebangenahb Ba Feere Kehnge A Ejira
\p 
\v 1 Atubesi abangenahb ba a, a ane ba abing ebo wob go awer nya ebangenahb ba mehle go Babilon jo feere kehnge aname ngare nyi ntula Ataseses jo fili edi:
\v 2 Go ebangenahb ji Finehas, Gersom; go ebangenahb ji Itama, Daniel; go ebangenahb ji Devid, Hatusi,
\v 3 ji lohng ebangenahb ji Sekanaya; go ebangenahb ji Parosi, Jakaraya, fvfo ane ba bo ko bo abing jolo aneblum atahl asehma, a aneblum awubu;
\v 4 go ebangenahb ji Pahati Moab, Eliehoenayi mmona Jerahiya, a aneblum atahl awubu ba jolo a ne;
\v 5 go ebangenahb ji Jatu, Sekaniya ji mmona Jahajiyel, a aneblum atahlku ba jolo a ne;
\v 6 go ebangenahb ji Adin, Ebed mmona Jonatan, a aneblum atahl abal, aneblum awubu ba jolo a ne;
\v 7 go ebangenahb ji Elam, Jesaya mmona Ataliya, a aneblum atahl ara, aneblum awubu ba jolo a ne;
\v 8 go ebangenahb ji Safatiya, Jabadiya mmona Mayikel, a aneblum atahl ani ba jolo a ne;
\v 9 go ebangenahb ji Joab, Obadiya mmona Jehiyel, a aneblum atahl awubu, a aneblum elku era ba jolo a ne;
\v 10 go ebangenahb ji Bani, Selomiti mmona Josifiya, a aneblum atahl anehkeni ba jolo a ne;
\v 11 go ebangenahb ji Bebayi, Jekaraya mmona Bebayi, a eltahl aneblum anehkeni ba jolo a ne;
\v 12 go ebangenahb ji Ajigad, Johanan mmona Hakatan, a aneblum atahl alon, aneblum awubu ba jolo a ne;
\v 13 go ebangenahb ji Adonikam, bo ji gohro ba, Elifeleti, Jewuyel, Semaya a aneblum atahl ara ba jolo a bo;
\v 14 go ebangenahb ji Bikvayi, Utayi, a Jakur, aneblum atahl ara, aneblum awubu ba jolo a bo.
\s1 Ejira Yehke anebe Levi Ba bahke Jo lim Eltum Etahk Esowo
\p 
\v 15 N kehm ba kono bo go efabalahb ji kpˈ fabe asongo go Ahava. E re ekv o nfung na era. N kehm jo feede go ellong ane a ellong abalimajom, nnea Levi awohng awohng o jolem.
\v 16 Owo n kehm lungu Elieja, Ariyel, Semaya, Elnatan, Jarib, Elnatan, Natan, Jekaraya, a Mesulam bo ji jolo atubesi, a Joiarib abola Elnatan bo ji jolo anebe ngbere,
\v 17 n fere tum bo tv Eddo, ntubesi no li go Kasifia. N tongo bo ji bo bahke song tong Eddo a akunu enye, a alokeltum go etahk Esowo ji li Kasifia, re bo ko abalimeltum ba ka-r ba bahke jo lim eltum go etahk Esowo ebahre.
\v 18 Tib nnoobo ebo bi Esowo ebahre bi jolo anahre, bo ko Serebiya ba ka-r, á jolo etingi nne no fuumu no, á lohng go ebangenahb ji Mahli mmona Levi, ji mmona Isreel. Bo tob ko abon ba nlum ba Serebiya ba, a abonanyehn, bo kpee jolo elku aneblum ara;
\v 19 a Hasabaya, a Jesaya ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Merari, a abonanyehn, a abon abonanyehn ba nlum, bo kpee jolo aneblum eltahl.
\v 20 Bo tob ko alokeltum go etahk Esowo, aneblum atahl ewubu ajehng, ane ba Devid a ane ba atubesi ane ebe ma yehke, re bo jo kak anebe Levi ebo. Bo kpee bo nyono abing ebo kpee go awer.
\s1 Ejira Tv Ane Go Njal Abade a Ero Akake
\p 
\v 21 O ebgba alahb bi Ahava, n tiingi bo re wahr jiin njal, eji e lꞌrede elnahre go esamahr Esowo ebahre. E kake ero bahb Esowo re á baab-r go mbang, a abon ebahre, a nsol kpee nyi e kpi no.
\v 22 Jol-m ejum ndon re me m bahb ntul bade nsoja, a ane ba kpo fing ebvankang, bo ji bahk-r baabe go esamahr anebekv ebahre go mbang, tib eji e ma tohko tong ntul re, <<Nnoobo ebo bi Esowo bahre kun nne awohng awohng no kpꞌkunu ekpu go ege, wo erakatahng eje li a ane kpee ma me-e ten>>.
\v 23 Ano wo e bade njal kak ero, bahb Esowo ebahre bade ejum jia, fvfo á faange ero ebahre.
\s1 Ayare Nya Li ka Etahk Esowo
\p 
\v 24 N kehm yehke atubesi abalimajom, ewubu ane abal, bo jolo Serebiya, Hasabaya, a ane awubu bako ba jolo abonanyehn ebo,
\v 25 fvfo n dumu nsol ka bo, ayare nya asilva, agul a ajoobo nsol nyako, nya ntul, atubu elle ebe, a atubesi, a anebe Isreel kpee ba jolo o ma ka go eltum etahk Esowo ebahre.
\v 26 N dumu nsol nyia kpee kehm faake kak bo go abo, ana wo jolo no: asilva jolo 22100 (ekilo atahltahl nkpel atahl abal a nkpel elku nkpel atahl alon), (nsol asilva nyako (3400 Atahltahl nkpel enehkeni atahl awubu) nya agul jolo 3400 atahltahl nkpel enehkeni atahl awubu.
\v 27 ekpeeke agul na eltahl, ekun ebe bahke rehnge akpohko agul atahltahl nkpel ebal atahl awubu.\f + \fr 8:27 \ft A lˈdumu bahke rehnge 8.5 kilogram \f* Anobo nobo nsol na abal nya bo ko abron nya bo ma dohk, jo nob ana agul.
\p 
\v 28 N kehm tongo abalimajom baa re, <<Wahn, a nsol nyia kpee, bo ma-n rod ka Jehova ana nsol nyi li saang. Asilva a agul, nya li nsol nyi ane ka go eboa eltim ka Jehova Esowo bi babnso ejahne.
\v 29 Baaben nsol nyia nobnob, tete wahn song dumu go ekpꞌkpa etahk ji Jehova go Jeusalem, go esamahr atubesi abalimajom, anebe Levi, a anebkul mfam ba Isreel.
\v 30 Owo abalimajom, a anebe Levi kehm koko asilva a agul, a nsol nyehko nyi li saang nyi bo ma dumu re bo sol tahm a nya go etahk Esowo ebahre ji li Jeusalem.
\s1 Anebe Isreel Feere Kehnge go Jeusalem
\p 
\v 31 Go ewuba nfung ebal mi ngbokambanga nnyahng, owo e mehle go ebgba bi Ahava asongo go Jeusalem. Ebo bi Esowo ebahre jolo anahre, jo baab-r fere tahr-r yehke go elwo ni anebekv ebahre, a abi ane go mbang.
\v 32 Ano wo e rehnge nobnob go Jeusalem, owo e re ekv nfung era.
\p 
\v 33 Eji ma rehng nfung eni nyi e rehnge Jeusalem, e kehm dumu asilva, agul, a nsol nyako nyi li saang, kehm faake kak Meremoti mmona Yuraya nlimanjom. Elieja mmona Finehas jolo o a ne, a anebe Levi fvfo, Jojabad mmona Jesua, a Noadiya mmona Binuyi.
\v 34 Ejum ajehng ajehng bo nyˈnyon kak ana go nfange no, fere dumu. Ellubu ene kpee bo nyˈnyon ngare nyio.
\p 
\v 35 Owo ane ba ma kehnge eju, kehm ba kehme ajom lim nya bo kpo jahm fi ka Esowo bi Isreel: Ewubu a nlum nfong ebal ka Isreel kpee, nkom atahl ani a nkom elku anyehng, abon ekom atahl ara abon ekom elku ebal. Bo wulu ewubu efahmbul ebbal tib go esi ajom nya abiafem. Nyaa kpee jolo njom nyi bo kpo jahm fi ka Jehova.
\v 36 Bo tob ka atubesi ane ba ntul jehke bo adi adi, a ane ba kpo fili erohko ji erede aya ma Yufritis ejehke ji ntul, bo ba jo tob ane, a etahk Esowo.
\c 9
\s1 Elkpane ni Ejira Kpane anebe Isreel Re Bo Kˈsong Ko Afi Bal Ane Ba ki li anebe Isreel
\p 
\v 1 Eji nsol nyia kpee ma lim, atubesi anebe Ju kehm ba kpir-m, fere tong-m re, <<Anebe Isreel, budu abalimajom, a anebe Levi ebten elyabe a anebe eltehb ba li sennge bo kak, ana anebe Kenan, Hiti, Pereji, Jebus, Amon, Moab, Ijib a anebe Amor.
\v 2 Bob song ko abon ebo bandiki ba nkal ana akal ebo, fere ko ka abon ebo ba nlum, bobfere semme elbo, bo ji li saang, a ane ba ki li saang ba li sennge bo kak. Wo atubesi, a abalimeltum ba ma sahb yˈyel rˈrahbe go ebˈbi jia.>>
\p 
\v 3 Eji n wuku jia, n kehm yare ewobo ejame a ekpawobo, fere tohng alvsi enyame woobo, a elahng, sa ji, eko ma-m tan.
\v 4 Nne awohng awohng no bele ekahmakahb go alum nyao nya Esowo bi Isreel, bo ba ji senng-m kak, tib go ekˈmal lim ji ane ba woomo eju . N ji ano eko ma-m tan tete ngare nyi bo kpo lim njom nyi elgung.
\p 
\v 5 Wo eji elgung ma ba ni bo kpo lim njom, n kehm mehle edi ji n ji no jo ling, ewobo a ekpawobo ejame ji ma yare, kehm gboko jamme alahng, tab abo enyame ton tv goji Jehova Esowo ebame,
\v 6 kak ero re: <<Esowo ebame, ndon kp-m fili sehng, li ejum esono re me n tab esamahr ebame seeng-a, Esowo ebame tibre abiafem enyahre ebwahre elkul sehnge asi enyahre, fvfo elsoodo ni e ma-a soodo ebrehng go elbung.
\v 7 Bomo afung nya babnsoo ejahre ji nkul tete rehng anv, nsoodo enyahre ebgbal area. Tib esi abiafem enyahre wahr, a atul ebahre, a abalimajom ebahre, bo kp-r wulu go ekahngkahng fere bob-r kak eju, kpur a nsol a nsol song nohk fere son-r go abo nya atul ajahmjahm, ana e li a lela.
\p 
\v 8 Wo anv, mmongare noa, Jehova Esowo ebahre e ma-a fili ndon re wo yak-r wahr sa mmorik ane ba li go elkpin. Á ma-r ka ebaabe ebjing ega mbarebare edi jia. Esowo ebahre ma-r ka ellennge go egahre amahr, fere yehk-r go eju abon afung baa.
\v 9 E jolo aju, Esowo ebahre wahr senngem njahm go eju ebahre, á ma-r tib nnoobo eljini ene, go esamahr atul ba Pesia : Á ma-r ka elkpin mfenfe re wahr tuungu etahk Esowo ebahre si, fere tob tuungu nsol etahk Esowo nyi ma rannge, fvfo á ma-r ka ekahme ji elbaabe go Juda a Jeusalem.
\p 
\v 10 Wo anv, Esowo ebahre, e bahke kpe bung jen toono nsol nyia? Tibre wahr ebten atahm enya,
\v 11 nya á ka-r no sehng go abo nya abanyehnamahr, ba jolo alokeltum eba, ngare nyi a bungu re, <<Edi ndi ji ń kpꞌyele, ebrannge tib ebi elkpin ni ane ba lene o. Bob rannge ndi go abꞌbi kpee, bomo go esi ejahbe jia song rehng esi ejahbe jehko.
\v 12 Fvfo kana yake abon ebahne ba nkal bo song bal abon ebo ba nlum, jol kana ko abon ebo ba nkal ka abon ebahne ba nlum. Kana ko nwongo nyi etem alimi a bo ngare anyehng anyehng, eji ń lꞌbel atahne, fere li anoobo nsol nya li go ndi nyia, fere yake ka abon ebahne go njinanjini ana ejum elehkelkv.
\p 
\v 13 <<Ejum ji ma-r lim a, lim-r tib esi abꞌbi enyahre, a egburu elsoodo enahre, jol fvfo Esowo ebahre, a ma-r kak erem bi rede sehnge abiafem enyahre, fere ka-r erik ane ana jia.
\v 14 Anv, wahr kpe ten atahm enya, fere song semme ane baa go elbala, bo ji kpꞌlimi elkohn ana niaa? Wo nehm bel erakatahng gbalee anahre ji á bahk-r rannge kpee, eji nnene lꞌkꞌkpe saa?
\v 15 Wo, Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, á li etingitingi Esowo! Lela wahr ebsa erik ane. Nyehn wahr a ma li ebi go ega esamahr, jol eji li etingitingi re nne no ma lim ebi ana jia, fuumem re á yiimi ega esamahr. esamahr.>>
\c 10
\s1 Ane fvvrv abiafem ebo
\p 
\v 1 Ngare nyi Ejira kpi nkake nkake ero fere jo fvvrv abiafem, jo ling fere jo bannge go ndi go mbuksong etahk Esowo, ellong anebe Isreel gbalee, aneblum, anebkal, a abonse abonse kehm bake ba senng-e kak. Bo tob lingi area.
\v 2 Owo Sekaniya mmona Jehiyel, ye ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Elam, kehm tongo Ejira re, <<Wahr limem ji Esowo ebahre tong-r no eji e ma tahm kpˈkoko anebkal ajahmjahm ba li senng-r kak. Wo jol, eji li li ano, ekunukpu jia ka anebe Isreel.
\v 3 Anv nong wahr limen egbanngalung go esamahr Esowo ebahre, song ten anebkal baa, fere kam bo, a abon abon ebo, ana elle ni Ejira nsoo ewame ka no, a elle ni ane ba kpˈfahle elkahn ni Esowo ebahre. Nong bo lim ana ntahm bungu no.
\v 4 Mehl yiimi, ntong nyia wob go ega abo. E bahk-a kake ebo, fvfo bob eltim wo lim.
\p 
\v 5 Ano wo Ejira mehle yiimi , kehm tongo atubesi abalimajom, a anebe Levi, go anebe Isreel kpee re bo ko nwongo re bo bahke limi ji bo ma toobo. Bo kehm koko nwongo.
\v 6 Wo Ejira kehm mehle go mbuksong etahk Esowo, song yel go ekpˈkpa ji Jehohanan mmona Eliasib. Eji Ejira jolo o, á tikem li ejum alehke ajehng ajehng, jol alahb á woom, tib á soro asi jo ling bade etahnsi ji ane ba ma kehnge eju.
\p 
\v 7 Owo bo kehm tiingi etib tv anebe Isreel kpee ba ma kehnge eju, go Juda a Jeusalem, re bo ba kono edi ajehng go Jeusalem.
\v 8 Nne awohng awohng no tohko lohng, go nfung era, bo bahk-e taare nsol enye kpee, jang jang ana anebkul a atubesi abalimeltum toobo no, wo yefono antahng bo bahke kame go ellong ane ba lohng eju.
\p 
\v 9 Go nfung era nyio, aneblum kpee ba Juda, a Benjamin kono go Jeusalem. Wo go nfung eltahl nyi nnyahng esehmwubu, ane kpee ji go elatahkgur, go mbuksong etahk Esowo, eko ma tan bo, tib esi nsol nyia, a eji elahb jo na.
\v 10 Owo Ejira nlimajom kehm mehle yiimi, tong bo re, <<Wahn nehme toono Esowo go mbang nyi nno, wahn ebsong ko anebkal ajahmjahm, kpe budu a nsoodo nyi Isreel ma soodo.
\v 11 Anv fvvren abiafem enyahne ka Jehova, Esowo bi babnso ejahne, wahn fere jo lim mbang enye. Yaben elnahne go ellong ane ba li senng-n kak, a akal ajahmjahm ebahne.>>
\p 
\v 12 Owo anebe Isreel kpee kehm taame fere jo rabe tiim re, <<Wob bung go nseenge; E bahke tiki lim ana a bungu no.
\v 13 Wo ane baa a gbalee, wo ga ngara nnale nyi; e nehm ma yiimi elatahk. Budu o, ntong nyia, a ntong efung abehng, afi nfung ebal sang, tibre wahr eblim abiafem nya gbale sehng go ejum jia.
\v 14 Nong atubesi abalimeltum ebahre lim nsol nyia go esi anebe Isreel kpee. Nong nne awohng awohng go egahre abon ajahbe, no ma ko nkal ajahmjahm, lohng go elatahkgur ekahme kahme ngare, a anebkul, go abalamalam ba ejahbe ajehng ajehng, tete egburu erakatahng ji Esowo ebahre bade ejum jia lohng-r go emel.>>
\v 15 Sehngem Jonatan mmona Asahel, a Jahjeya mmona Tikva bo ba ki taame, wo Mesulam abola Sabetayi anebe Levi tob toono bo ten.
\p 
\v 16 Ano wo ane ba kehnge eju limi ji bo toobo no. Ejira ji nlimanjom kehm jake aneblum ba li atubesi ebangenahb yehke, nne awohng go ebangenahb ajehng ajehng, no nne jo yiimi go ege a mbing. Go ngbokambang efung bi nnyahng ewubu, bo ba ji jo feede alamlam nyaa,
\v 17 re kehm rehnge go ngbokambang efung bi ngbokambanga nnyahng, bo male ntoobo bade aneblum kpee ba ko akal ajahmjahm.
\s1 Aneblum Ba Baange Akal Ajahmjahm
\p 
\v 18 Go ellong ebangenahb ji abalimajom, ane ba a, ba baange akal ajahmjahm: Go ebangenahb ji Jesua mmona Jojadak, a abonanyehn ba nlum: Maaseya, Elieja, Jarib, a Gadaliya.
\v 19 Bo kpee taame ko nwongo re bo bahke yehke akal ebo go elbal, go ebi ji bo ma li, no nne ka nkom, go ellong ejoro ana njom nyi bo ma li ebi.
\p 
\v 20 Go ebangenahb ji Imer: Hanani abola Jebadiya.
\p 
\v 21 Go ebangenahb ji Harim: Maaseya, Elaija, Semaiya, Jehiyel, a Ujiya.
\p 
\v 22 Go ebangenahb ji Pashur: Elioyenayi, Maaseya, Ismeel, Netanel, Jojabad, a Elasa.
\p 
\v 23 Go ellong anebe Levi: Jojabad, Simeyi, Kelaya (ji li Kelita), Petahiya, Juda, a Elieja.
\p 
\v 24 Go ellong abayimasene: Eliasib. Go ellong ababˈbaabe ati mbu: Salum, Telem, a Uri.
\p 
\v 25 Go ellong anebe Isreel bako: Go ebangenahb ji Parosi: Ramiya, Ijiya, Malikija, Mijamin, Elieja, Malikija a Benaya.
\p 
\v 26 Go ebangenahb ji Elam: Mataniya, Jekaraya, Jehiyel, Abidi, Jeremoti, a Elaija.
\p 
\v 27 Go ebangenahb ji Jatu: Elioyenayi, Eliasib, Mataniya, Jeremoti, Jabad, a Ajija.
\p 
\v 28 Go ebangenahb ji Bebayi: Jehohanan, Hananiya, Jabayi, a Atilayi.
\p 
\v 29 Go ebangenahb ji Bani: Mesulam, Maluk, Adaya, Jasub, Seyal, a Jeremoti.
\p 
\v 30 Go ebangenahb ji Pahati Moab: Adina, Kelal, Benaya, Maaseya, Mataniya, Bejalel, Binuyi, a Manase.
\p 
\v 31 Go ebangenahb ji Harim: Elieja, Isija, Malikija, Semaya, Simion,
\v 32 Benjamin, Maluk, a Semariya.
\p 
\v 33 Go ebangenahb ji Hasum: Matenayi, Matata, Jabad, Elifeleti, Jeremayi, Manase, a Simeyi.
\p 
\v 34 Go ebangenahb ji Bani: Maadayi, Amiram, Yuwel ,
\v 35 Benaya, Bedeya, Keluhi,
\v 36 Vaniya, Meremoti, Eliasib,
\v 37 Mataniya, Matenayi, a Jaasu.
\p 
\v 38 Go ebangenahb ji Binuyi: Simeyi,
\v 39 Selemiya, Natan, Adaya.
\v 40 Makinadebayi, Sasayi, Sarayi,
\v 41 Ajarel, Selemaya, Semariya,
\v 42 Salum, Amariya, a Josef.
\p 
\v 43 Go ebangenahb ji Nebo: Jeyel Matitiya, Jabad, Jebina, Jadayi, Jowel, a Benaya.
\p 
\v 44 Anenlum baa kpee baange akal ajahmjahm, fvfo bo jindiki akal baa ebjel abon ka bo.
